---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Physique Photography
metaTitle: "Physique & Competition Photography — Nashville"
metaDescription: "Professional physique photography for bodybuilding competitors. Pre-show, post-show, and transformation sessions. Shot by a fellow competitor who understands the sport."
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="fade-in">Physique & Fitness</h1>
    <p class="tagline fade-in">You Didn't Train This Hard for Average Photos.</p>
    <div class="intro-text fade-in" style="max-width: 750px; margin: var(--space-md) auto 0;">
      <p>Professional physique photography for competitors who want images as sharp as their conditioning. You've spent months dialing in your nutrition, perfecting your posing, and pushing through workouts that would break most people. As a bodybuilder who's stood on stage himself, I understand the work — and I know how lighting, angles, and posing direction can make the difference between a good photo and one that truly captures what you've built.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== BLACK & WHITE GALLERY ===== #}
<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title fade-in">
      <h2>Black & White</h2>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid stagger-children">
      {% set bwImages = [
        { src: "hero_shot_bw_04290", alt: "Hero Shot — Black & White" },
        { src: "arnold_bw_04277", alt: "Arnold Pose — Black & White" },
        { src: "bw_front_double_biceps_04236", alt: "Front Double Biceps" },
        { src: "bw_back_double_biceps_04248", alt: "Back Double Biceps" },
        { src: "bw_front_pose_04233", alt: "Front Pose" },
        { src: "open_jacket_bw_05012", alt: "Open Jacket" },
        { src: "looking_down_bw_04326", alt: "Looking Down" },
        { src: "bw_04836", alt: "Studio Portrait" },
        { src: "bw_04899", alt: "Studio Pose" },
        { src: "pockets_bw_04811", alt: "Pockets" }
      ] %}
      {% for img in bwImages %}
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/physique-bw/{{ img.src }}-800w.webp 800w, /images/physique-bw/{{ img.src }}-1200w.webp 1200w, /images/physique-bw/{{ img.src }}-1920w.webp 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (max-width: 1000px) 50vw, 33vw" type="image/webp">
          <img src="/images/physique-bw/{{ img.src }}-1200w.webp" alt="{{ img.alt }}" loading="lazy">
        </picture>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# ===== COLOR GALLERY ===== #}
<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title fade-in">
      <h2>Color</h2>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="gallery-grid stagger-children">
      {% set colorImages = [
        { src: "hero_shot_1_04290", alt: "Hero Shot — Color" },
        { src: "arnold_04277", alt: "Arnold Pose" },
        { src: "front_double_biceps_04236", alt: "Front Double Biceps" },
        { src: "back_double_biceps_04248", alt: "Back Double Biceps" },
        { src: "front_pose_04233", alt: "Front Pose" },
        { src: "hero_shot_look_2_04318", alt: "Hero Shot Look 2" },
        { src: "open_jacket_05012", alt: "Open Jacket" },
        { src: "looking_down_04326", alt: "Looking Down" },
        { src: "dsc04836", alt: "Studio Portrait" },
        { src: "dsc04899", alt: "Studio Pose" },
        { src: "pockets_04811", alt: "Pockets" }
      ] %}
      {% for img in colorImages %}
      <div class="gallery-item">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/physique-color/{{ img.src }}-800w.webp 800w, /images/physique-color/{{ img.src }}-1200w.webp 1200w, /images/physique-color/{{ img.src }}-1920w.webp 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, (max-width: 1000px) 50vw, 33vw" type="image/webp">
          <img src="/images/physique-color/{{ img.src }}-1200w.webp" alt="{{ img.alt }}" loading="lazy">
        </picture>
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section section-dark">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title fade-in" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center;">
      <h2>Sessions start at $400</h2>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      <p>Every session is tailored to your physique and goals.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: var(--space-md);">
        <a href="/contact/?service=physique" class="btn btn-fill">Get a Quote →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title fade-in">
      <h2>The Process</h2>
      <div class="gold-divider"></div>
      <p>From first message to final delivery</p>
    </div>
    <div class="process-grid stagger-children">
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-number">01</div>
        <h3>Book</h3>
        <p>Reach out through the contact form or DM. Tell me about your show, your timeline, and what you're looking for.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-number">02</div>
        <h3>Consult</h3>
        <p>We'll discuss your goals, posing preferences, location options, and the look you're going for. I'll help you plan the perfect session.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-number">03</div>
        <h3>Shoot</h3>
        <p>Show up, bring your best. I handle the lighting, direction, and energy. You focus on showing off the physique you've built.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="process-step">
        <div class="process-number">04</div>
        <h3>Deliver</h3>
        <p>Professionally edited images delivered to your private online gallery within 7–10 business days. Social-media-ready files included.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

